Here's a PlantUML sequence diagram representing the data flow in the smev3_adapter_service system:

```plantuml
@startuml s-sokolko_smev3_adapter_service

participant "Client" as client
participant "API Layer\n(views.py)" as api
participant "QueryProcessor\n(processors/query.py)" as processor
participant "Adapter\n(adapter.py)" as adapter
participant "SMEV3 Adapter" as smev3
database "MongoDB" as db
participant "SchemaLoader\n(schema_loader/loader.py)" as loader

client -> api : POST /schedule_query/<query_type>/
activate api

api -> processor : process_query(query_type, data)
activate processor

processor -> loader : load_schema(query_type)
activate loader
loader --> processor : schema
deactivate loader

processor -> adapter : send_request(query_type, data)
activate adapter

adapter -> smev3 : SOAP request
activate smev3
smev3 --> adapter : SOAP response
deactivate smev3

adapter --> processor : response
deactivate adapter

processor -> db : save_query(query)
activate db
db --> processor : query_id
deactivate db

processor --> api : query_id
deactivate processor

api --> client : query_id
deactivate api

...

client -> api : GET /get_document/<query_type>/<query_id>/
activate api

api -> db : get_query(query_id)
activate db
db --> api : query
deactivate db

api -> processor : check_response(query)
activate processor

alt response not ready
    processor -> adapter : get_response(query)
    activate adapter
    adapter -> smev3 : SOAP request
    activate smev3
    smev3 --> adapter : SOAP response
    deactivate smev3
    adapter --> processor : response
    deactivate adapter

    processor -> db : update_query(query, response)
    activate db
    db --> processor : updated_query
    deactivate db
end

processor --> api : document or status
deactivate processor

api --> client : document or status
deactivate api

@enduml
```

This sequence diagram illustrates the data flow in the smev3_adapter_service system, focusing on two main operations: scheduling a query and retrieving a document. It shows the interactions between the client, API layer, QueryProcessor, Adapter, SMEV3 Adapter, MongoDB, and SchemaLoader components.